gw.api.profiler

Class ProfilerStack

  • gw.api.profiler.ProfilerStack

  • public class ProfilerStack

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      ProfilerFrame EntryPointFrame
      The entry point frame.
      String EntryPointName
      The entry point name.
      int FrameCount
      Returns the number of frames in this stack
      Set<ProfilerStack> SpawnedStacks
      Returns a list of ProfilerStacks for each of the threads spawned by the thread associated with this stack.
      String StackName
      Returns PCF location information in the form "from -> to"
      long StartTime
      Returns the time when the stack started
      int TotalElapsedTime
      Returns the difference between the time when the top frame was pushed and when it was popped. If the top frame hasn't been popped, or if the stack is empty, returns -1. This is the same as the elapsed time of the entry point frame.
